	//wizard hell of my own making
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT1.Base": "Blasted thing, where did it... Oh, it's you.$0#$b#Should you see a stray junimo around my tower today... Please inform me, posthaste.$0",
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT2.Base": "%The wizard is attempting to avoid your gaze.#$e#Let us not speak of what happened yesterday, farmer. I underestimated the spirits' ability to pull pranks...$0#$b#A minor embarassment is the price I have paid. Begone for today, if you would.$0",
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT1.SVE": "Blasted thing, where did it... Oh, it's you.$4#$b#Should you see a stray junimo around my tower today... Please inform me, posthaste.$0",
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT2.SVE": "%The wizard is attempting to avoid your gaze.#$e#Let us not speak of what happened yesterday, farmer. I underestimated the spirits' ability to pull pranks...$3#$b#A minor embarassment is the price I have paid. Begone for today, if you would.$0",
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT1.RRRR": "Blasted thing, where did it... Oh, it's you.$11#$b#Should you see a stray junimo around my tower today... Please inform me, posthaste.$10",
	"Wizard.JunimoMailCT2.RRRR": "%The wizard is attempting to avoid your gaze.#$e#Let us not speak of what happened yesterday, farmer. I underestimated the spirits' ability to pull pranks...$3#$b#A minor embarassment is the price I have paid. Begone for today, if you would.$0",
	"Wizard.ChainLetterCT.Base": "The concept of a 'chain letter demon' is absurd. There is not a single binding rune on this page, nor has it been writ in enchanted ink...!$0#$b#The work of this scroll is less than amateur.$0",
	"Wizard.ChainLetterCT.SVE": "",
	"Wizard.ChainLetterCT.RRRR": "",
	"Wizard.GameTheoryCT.Base": "You have a strange expression on your face today, @.$0#$b#Ah... It would appear that the more mundane folk are catching onto the existence of the veil.$0#$b#I suggest you pay it no mind, as what lies beyond it cannot be changed by us in any meaningful fashion. Go on, carry on with your day.$0",
	"Wizard.GameTheoryCT.SVE": "",
	"Wizard.GameTheoryCT.RRRR": "",
	"Wizard.LotteryWinnerCT.Base": "It would appear that a statistical anomaly has occured in the area. I assure you, I had nothing to do with this.$0#$b#One of the first lessons a mage learns is not to mess with Lady Luck...$0",
	"Wizard.LotteryWinnerCT.SVE": "",
	"Wizard.LotteryWinnerCT.RRRR": "",
	"Wizard.ClownCollegeCT.Base": "I heard you have been contacted by... Bumblefun. He is not to be trusted, though you'd be better under my tutelage anyway.$0#$b#Oh? Was the letter sent to you in error, you think?$0#$b#Ah. Well, my offer still stands. Perhaps another time, @.$0",
	"Wizard.ClownCollegeCT.SVE": "",
