	//Solarion Online, a joke riffing on the ff14 copypasta. Gamers(tm) would likely respond to this
	"Abigail.SolarionCT": "Do you play Solarion Online, @? A couple of us play together on the weekends.$0#$b#I used to be the healer, but smacking around monsters with a big axe is a lot more fun!$1",
	"Jodi.SolarionCT": "Vincent keeps asking me about some computer game that Sam plays with his friends.$0#$b#I think he's still too young for that, but it is cute when Sam lets him try it out for a bit.$1",
	"Sam.SolarionCT": "Yeah, I play Solarion with the other guys... But I always end up being the healer.$2#$b#I don't mind it, but I'd rather be a bard or something...$2#$b#At least I get dibs on the cool loot, though.$1",
	"Sebastian.SolarionCT": "Solarion Online is pretty cool...$0#$b#Nothing beats the fun of the original, but it's a lot easier to play online with friends, y'know?$2#$b#I think Sam's a little tired of playing the healer if you ever want to join our guild.$1",
	//todo: maybe make this one dynamic based on Chocobo Valley detection?
	"Vincent.SolarionCT": "Big birds! Sam has a real big bird in his computer game.$1#$b#I wanna ride one... Are there big birds on your farm? Can you show me?$0",
	//sve
	"Sophia.SolarionCT": "My Solarion character cosplays too! Dressing her up is pretty fun.$8#$b#I kinda wish the developers would stop changing the Marksman class so often though... I liked the way it was in Stormbreaker.$2#$b#Maybe I should try playing something new, like a healer?$9",
	"Victor.SolarionCT": "I don't know if you knew this, but Sebastian is quite the role-player.$4#$b#'Sir Victor, this staff you made for me is of excellent quality... As guildmaster, I applaud your great work...'$0#$b#It certainly makes the game more interesting.$1",
	
